==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unclutch
<hw>Un*clutch"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>clutch</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To open, as
something closely shut.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Unclutch</xex> his griping
hand.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Dr. H. More.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Mech.)</fld> <def>To disengage, as a
clutch.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unco</ent>⟦br⟧
